profile:
Lush Designs was born out of a passion for design and a love for all of the finer things in life.

We have been renovating and designing homes for well over a decade and that love for quality products grew into opening a custom millwork company. We know details and more importantly, we fully comprehend how things are manufactured.

We see interior design as a work of art and we only partner with clients who appreciate the environments we produce. We know how to help you develop a healthy budget for your project, indentify the needs and desires of your space, determine workable designs and ultimately execute those visions through delivery and installation.

We bring a set of fresh eyes to every space and can contribue new ideas that may not have been dreamt of. We look at the functionality of any space and ensure that we maximize every square inch so that your life becomes clutter free and systemized in a way that makes sense. We ensure that things go right the first time and everyone is held accountable for their timelines. In essence, we handle all of the stress so you can enjoy the process of your brand new space.

Lets see if we are a good fit, contact us today to get started.
